{"tid":605933,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［暗瘡印煩惱］有冇人試過做激光？","createTime":"2018-03-26T05:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T17:50:38.000Z","uid":77086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4bccc0f517c21867acd2aed9ac5ab3ce06600b5","tid":605933,"uid":77086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"以前青春期果時都冇乜點生暗瘡 食幾多炸野都冇事<br />\n反而宜家20、21歲居然係咁生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我塊面係冇暗瘡 全部暗瘡都係聚集係嘴邊同鼻<br />\n我生既暗瘡無論搞佢定唔搞佢 都會有印<br />\n我以前成日素顏出街..宜家我素顏連落街都唔敢<br />\n日日帶口罩 因為我宜家真係成個污嘴狗咁<br />\n我d印有d係中間仲有白色咁 但係點都支唔到野出黎<br />\n有d就紅紫 咁既印..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD印真係非常影響我 搞到我冇晒自信 又成日好唔開心<br />\n已經買左超多去印既膏 又成日敷面膜<br />\n但係完全改善唔到 到宜家都係不斷生新既暗瘡 <br />\n同埋留新既印........<br />\n<br />\n最近成日睇到好多激光去印 但係又有好多種 <br />\n我剩係想去暗瘡印 唔洗去凹凸印 斑 美白果d<br />\n究竟邊種岩我？<br />\n跪求救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b6c1011864b4c494ed3469ecc7ccb4c7ecdca6","tid":605933,"uid":77086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00ec9e59131d0a07328e72107814cb214de91d2","tid":605933,"uid":77086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"冇人生暗瘡"},{"pid":"a87f018a257b272133b3863369ea99017d502078","tid":605933,"uid":727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"Me u can see my post"},{"pid":"85aa6692c74435acbbb18870359fbf9179c0340d","tid":605933,"uid":150881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"生喺咀同鼻喺關身體唔健康事 生喺面就青春期 生喺額頭喺唔夠訓"},{"pid":"2266b193e898a2d212772ef83acf1ca08b81896d","tid":605933,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"