e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"其實印既話做PEELING就搞店~"},{"pid":"e2344292962f0491b02653c147d7e2acf9450d07","tid":605933,"uid":131552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"唔洗太擔心 如果係凹凸仲慘啊!!"},{"pid":"0f65b69695f32ddd60af561a0d0677649b510072","tid":605933,"uid":175719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"其實係咪真係work㗎 同埋幾錢㗎 後生嗰時瘋狂生暗瘡 成身無忽好肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd95b4b786628690b21376aeb2b58294327fb4f","tid":605933,"uid":134201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"有d印起碼搞幾個月先退 千奇唔好心急 d skincare盡量用少d<br />\n<br />\n樓主試下用玫瑰果油搽落瘡印位到<br />\n我試左2個星期 d印係淡左d 相信長遠用會淡 我記得好似話最少要用4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玫瑰果油始終好油 我只敢搽係印同疤既位置"}]}